value:
The training sessions covered the following topics:
- Overview of the mutual fund industry and the Company’s business model;
- Key systems and policies implemented by the Company;
- Updates on Indian and global markets;
- Corporate governance framework;
- Risk management framework;
- Digitisation of business processes;
- Management structure, HR policies, management development, and succession planning;
- Review of Internal Audit;
- Operations of subsidiaries;
- Update on digital marketing;
- ESG activities, etc.
These trainings contributed to enhancing the effectiveness of the Board and strengthening the Company’s overall governance
practices.

The topics of the training were as follows:
- Prevention of Sexual Harassment;
- Code of Ethics;
- Anti-Money Laundering;
- Whistleblower;
- Diversity, Equity, & Inclusion;
- Information Security Awareness; and
- Environment, Social, & Governance

